Package civitas.celestis.util.grid

Interface Grid<E>

Type Parameters:
E - The type of element this grid should hold
All Superinterfaces:
Iterable<E>, Serializable
All Known Subinterfaces:
NumericGrid<N,M>
All Known Implementing Classes:
ArrayGrid, LongGrid, Matrix, SyncGrid
public interface Grid<E> extends Iterable<E>, Serializable
A two-dimensional structure of objects. Grids can be traversed by either providing two separate indices for the row and column, or by providing am Index object.
